        "id": 1003211
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-12-07T03:45:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If from_text is empty it\u0027s a bad rpc. Since from_text is oneof with from_file, this means from_text must be specified and from_file must not be specified. So if the caller specifies from_file: \"key:filename\" it will say \"from text must be in key:value form\" hinting that from_text must be given, which implies that from_file must not be given.",
